sentences.english: They could even count the fruit in Soviet orchards and analyze their crops.
sentences.chinese: 他们甚至可以数出苏联果园里的果树并分析其产量。

sentences.english: Jia-wen Luo do the experimental investigation and make a research summary and finish the research report.

sentences.english: He self-reflected and decided to decrease the stress and clean up his diet, looking beyond the status quo.
sentences.chinese: 他能自我反醒并决定减少压力和调整饮食，改变现状。

sentences.english: Life won't always turn out the way you want.
sentences.chinese: 生活并不总会如你所愿。

sentences.english: Miss Athill did not keep the letters she received from Mr Field.
sentences.chinese: 阿西尔女士并没有保留菲尔德先生写给她的信件。

sentences.english: Shows how to open a port and communicate wih other computers.
sentences.chinese: 这个程序演示了打开一个端口，并和其它计算机通信。

sentences.english: Meditation can help, and should be your first choice before medication.
sentences.chinese: 沉思能帮助你并应该是你就医前的首选。

sentences.english: I ain't so very drunk, Melly.
sentences.chinese: 我并没有那么醉，梅勒妮。

sentences.english: Newton's law is not applicable to any case.
sentences.chinese: 牛顿定律并不适合于任何情况。

sentences.english: First impressions of Sumatra are not good.
sentences.chinese: 苏门答腊给我的第一印象并不好。

sentences.english: The line was going out fast but steadily and the fish was not panicked.
sentences.chinese: 钓索朝水中溜得既快又稳，阐明这鱼并不受惊。

sentences.english: According to Zhao, life in military campsites is not monotonous.
sentences.chinese: 赵峰表示，军营生活并不单调。

sentences.english: Mengsk approached the smaller man and stood before him, an intimidating presence.
sentences.chinese: 蒙克斯以威迫的姿态靠近并站在这位小矮人前面。

sentences.english: When finished with the list, click OK then close out of Local Group Policy Editor.
sentences.chinese: 完成列表后，点击确定并关闭本地组策略编辑器。

sentences.english: Melbury did not seem to be particularly enlightened by this explanation.
sentences.chinese: 麦尔布礼看来对这个解释并不很明白。
